<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA10">
<l>tēcun tiṟalun tiruvu muruvamu</l>
<l>mācil kuṭippiṟappu maṟṟavaiyum – pēcil</l>
<l>valampurinta vāṉcaṅkaṅ koṇṭāṉpē rōta</l>
<l>nalampurintu ceṉṟaṭaiyu naṉku</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Speaking of light, power, wealth and beauty,</l>
<l>birth in a flawless family and other things</l>
<l>– when one recites the names of him who held the right-spiralling pure conch,</l>
<l>those will do good, go [and] well reach [him].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
